I will handle it.

20:00.333 --> 20:01.568
- Ah, that terrifies me.

20:01.601 --> 20:05.838
- [sighs]
I know.

20:05.872 --> 20:07.940
- This is so messed up.

20:07.974 --> 20:11.678
- Yeah.
