Isn't that right, Ruby?

20:33.032 --> 20:34.667
- That's right.

20:34.701 --> 20:36.703
- She's gonna have to say
a little bit more than that.

20:36.736 --> 20:38.471
- All due respect--
- I'm sorry.

20:38.505 --> 20:41.474
This woman was careless
and rude and hurt my son.

20:41.508 --> 20:42.475
- No--wait a minute.

20:42.509 --> 20:44.311
Your son hurt himself.

20:44.344 --> 20:48.748
- You went out of your way not
to warn him that plate was hot.

20:48.781 --> 20:49.982
- Are you for real?

20:50.016 --> 20:52.819
- Just say you're sorry.

20:52.852 --> 20:54.020
