20:54.053 --> 20:55.788
- And yet we still
haven't heard it.

20:55.822 --> 20:57.790
Do you all have children?
- I do.

20:57.824 --> 21:01.561
- Look at the example
you're setting.

21:01.594 --> 21:03.863
- [mouthing words]

21:03.896 --> 21:06.799
*

21:06.833 --> 21:08.368
- I'm sorry.

21:08.401 --> 21:09.569
Okay?

21:09.602 --> 21:11.371
- Thank you, Ruby.
- It's not okay.

21:11.404 --> 21:14.040
