21:38.365 --> 21:41.568
and how to treat anyone--
especially service people--

21:41.601 --> 21:42.802
with respect.

21:42.835 --> 21:44.837
- She doesn't mean that.
- No, I do.

21:44.871 --> 21:46.906
I am one sorry bitch.
- Ah...

21:46.939 --> 21:49.542
- I'm sorry you have your head
so far up your ass

21:49.576 --> 21:51.411
that you think it's okay
to blame everyone else

21:51.444 --> 21:53.646
for your son being a moron.

21:53.680 --> 21:56.749
I'm sorry he's such
a punk-ass bitch

21:56.783 --> 21:59.886
because that is a surface burn.

21:59.919 --> 22:03.656
And I am especially sorry that
the friends you bring in here

22:03.690 --> 22:08.027
are as entitled and as spoiled
and as awful as you,

22:08.060 --> 22:11.097
because if kids like you all
are our future,

22:11.130 --> 22:13.099
God help us all.

22:13.132 --> 22:15.568
Now, that's what
I'm sorry about.

