Right?
[chuckles]

26:04.263 --> 26:05.331
What?
I'm just--

26:05.364 --> 26:06.733
I'm just saying, you know.

26:06.766 --> 26:09.669
You want fun,
you rob a grocery store.

26:09.702 --> 26:10.603
- Hey!

26:10.637 --> 26:13.840
