minimum wage.

26:13.873 --> 26:19.912
all: * Happy birthday,
dear Kenny *

26:19.946 --> 26:24.250
* Happy birthday to you

26:24.283 --> 26:25.885
[cheers and applause]

26:25.918 --> 26:28.220
- Yeah, whoo, whoo, whoo!
